# Bronze: raw DepEd source files (large, externally-sourced, not committed)
data/bronze/**
!data/bronze/README.md
!data/bronze/frozen/
!data/bronze/frozen/README.md
!data/bronze/live/
!data/bronze/live/README.md

# Reference: external reference data (e.g. PSA shapefile; too large to commit)
data/reference/**
!data/reference/README.md

